---
import { personal } from "../data/content";
---

<section id="about" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 border-t border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-light tracking-tight text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 mb-6">About</h2>
  <div class="max-w-2xl text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
    <p>
      I'm the sole data hire at Anatomy Financial, which means I own everything from data
      modelling and dbt development to Sigma dashboards and pipeline orchestration with
      Meltano and Temporal. Right now I'm diving head first into Claude Code for
      agent-driven development, leading a PostgreSQL to Redshift migration, and
      continuing to ship the data products the business runs on.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before that I worked across healthcare and retail, building reporting platforms,
      running statistical analysis, and scaling automated client reporting. I hold an
      Advanced dbt Certification from Uplimit, a Data Science certificate from UCSC
      Extension, and a Master's in Economics and Geography from the University of Aberdeen.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
